OL,3,CMother, 55, spared jailed for killing
OL,4,Cbaby boy almost 30 years ago
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports Tasha Kacheri
OL,7,Ftells the story of Joanne Sharkey, who
OL,8,Fkept the secret for almost 30 years
OL,10,FA mother who admitted killing her
OL,11,Fnewborn son more than 25 years ago has
OL,12,Fbeen spared jailed after a judge said
OL,13,Fher case called "for compassion".
OL,15,FThe body of baby Callum - named by the
OL,16,Fofficers who worked on the case - was
OL,17,Ffound in a bin bag in woods near
OL,18,FGulliver's World in Warrington in 1998.
