OL,3,CMother, 55, spared jailed for killing
OL,4,Cbaby boy almost 30 years ago
OL,6,FJoanne Sharkey, 55, remained
OL,7,Funidentified until 2023, when her
OL,8,Feldest son's DNA was added to the
OL,9,Fpolice database, leading to her arrest.
OL,11,FThe mum, from Croxteth, in Merseyside,
OL,12,Fdenied murder but pleaded guilty to
OL,13,Fthe lesser charge of manslaughter on
OL,14,Fthe basis of diminished responsibility
OL,15,Fand concealing the birth of a child.
