OL,4,Cbaby boy almost 30 years ago
OL,6,FSentencing her at Liverpool Crown
OL,7,FCourt, Mrs Justice Eady told Sharkey
OL,8,Fshe was satisfied "depression and the
OL,9,Ftrauma of the birth substantially
OL,10,Fimpaired your ability to understand
OL,11,Fthe nature and consequences of your
OL,12,Factions."
OL,14,FWhile, she said, Sharkey's offending
OL,15,Fcrossed the custody threshold, she
OL,16,Fbelieved she "presented no danger or
OL,17,Frisk to the public".
