OL,6,FPolice bodycam footage shows the
OL,7,Fmoment Joanne Sharkey was arrested on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of killing and concealing
OL,9,Fthe birth of her baby boy in 1998.
OL,11,FHanding her two years in prison,
OL,12,Fsuspended for two years, Mrs Justice
OL,13,FEady said: "I cannot avoid the
OL,14,Fconclusion that a custodial term is
OL,15,Fthe appropriate disposal.
