OL,6,FShe was also given a rehabilitation
OL,7,Factivity requirement of up to 30 days
OL,8,Fand a 12-month mental health treatment
OL,9,Frequirement.
OL,11,FLiverpool Crown Court previously heard
OL,12,Fthe body of the infant was found in a
OL,13,Fbin bag by walkers on 14 March 1998.
OL,15,FDetectives named the infant Callum,
OL,16,Fafter the suburb where he was found
OL,17,Fdead, and was believed to have been
OL,18,Fjust a few hours old.
