OL,6,FThe court heard when Sharkey killed
OL,7,Fthe baby, she was suffering from post-
OL,8,Fnatal depression after the birth of
OL,9,Fher first son, Matthew, in 1996.
OL,11,FMr Hankin said psychiatrists agreed
OL,12,FSharkey was "fearful of becoming a
OL,13,Fmother to another child" and developed
OL,14,Fa depressive illness which
OL,15,F"substantially impaired (her) ability
OL,16,Fto form rational judgement and
OL,17,Fexercise self-control".
