OL,4,Cbaby boy almost 30 years ago
OL,6,FShe told police she kept her pregnancy
OL,7,Fa secret and, when the baby was born
OL,8,Fin the bathroom of her house in
OL,9,FCroxteth, Liverpool, she heard him
OL,10,Fstarting to make a noise and covered
OL,11,Fhis nose and mouth "to make him quiet".
OL,13,FIn her interviews with police, Sharkey
OL,14,Fdescribed her state of mind at the
OL,15,Fprospect of a second child as a case
OL,16,Fof "I can't do this again", the court
OL,17,Fheard.
OL,19,FShe said she kept her pregnancy a
OL,20,Fsecret by wearing bigger clothes and
OL,21,Fkeeping everyone "at arm's length".
