OL,6,FSharkey told officers the labour,
OL,7,Fwhich she thought had happened in the
OL,8,Fbathroom, was "easy and quick" and she
OL,9,Fwas the only person in the house at
OL,10,Fthe time.
OL,12,FShe told police: "I sort of reached
OL,13,Fdown. I must have been on the floor at
OL,14,Fthis point. I've covered his nose, his
OL,15,Fmouth. It just couldn't make that
OL,16,Fnoise, just to be quiet."
OL,18,FSharkey replied "no comment" when
OL,19,Fasked about the wads of tissue and
OL,20,Fbruising to the baby's head and neck.
