OL,6,FShe then drove to Warrington to
OL,7,Fdispose of the child.
OL,9,FLater she told detectives: "It's
OL,10,Fhaunting, something you think about
OL,11,Fevery day. You try and push it out but
OL,12,Fit creeps back in. You carry on with
OL,13,Fyour life, you go to work and you do
OL,14,FChristmas and you do Easter but this
OL,15,Fis always in your head."
OL,17,FAt an earlier hearing, both Sharkey's
OL,18,Fhusband and son spoke in support of
OL,19,Fthe mum, with statements from the pair
OL,20,Fread out in court.
