OL,6,FA statement from Neil Sharkey said he
OL,7,Fwas "not the greatest husband and
OL,8,Ffather" when he was younger and
OL,9,FSharkey had "single-handedly raised
OL,10,FMatthew to be one of the nicest people
OL,11,FI've known".
OL,13,FThe statement read: "I blame myself
OL,14,Ffor what happened as I was not the
OL,15,Feasiest person to live with... I'm
OL,16,Fsupporting Joanne and always will."
OL,18,FWhile a statement from Matthew said:
OL,19,F"We as a family are supporting my mum
OL,20,Fand standing by her.
