OL,6,F"I will always support my mum and
OL,7,Fstand by her as she is my mum and I am
OL,8,Faware she was mentally ill at the
OL,9,Ftime."
OL,11,FThe court heard two doctors gave the
OL,12,Fbaby's medical cause of death as
OL,13,F"unascertained" and could not
OL,14,Fdetermine whether he had been alive
OL,15,Fwhen the tissue was put in his mouth.
OL,17,FNina Grahame KC, defending Sharkey,
OL,18,Fsaid: "Were it not for her mental
OL,19,Fillness it is inconceivable a woman
OL,20,Fsuch as Mrs Sharkey would have failed
OL,21,Fto care for her newborn child."
